# 🚀 Smart Job Application Tracker

A responsive web application built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript to efficiently track job applications and monitor progress.

---

 Live Demo

🔗 **[Click Here to View Live Project]( https://thanish-dev.github.io/smart-job-application-tracker/)**

---

## ✨ Features

- Add and Delete Job Applications
- Search by Company Name
- Filter by Application Status
- Real-time Dashboard Statistics
- LocalStorage Data Persistence
- Fully Responsive Layout

---

## 🛠 Tech Stack

- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript 

